description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Direct Commissioning Team (Midlands Region) to cover the role Contract Support Officer -Primary Dental, Care – East Midlands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic, motivated and enthusiastic individual to join the Secondary Dental Care Commissioning Team, operating within the wider East Midlands Pharmacy, Optometry and Dental (PODs) team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will work as part of a highly productive team in delivering an effective service, supporting managers and staff across the locality to commission/transform services. The ideal candidate will need to embrace change, be flexible in approach and have a passion for innovation as we move forward with implementing the priorities outlined in the Long-Term Plan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will provide and coordinate administrative and secretarial services to the team and consistently deliver a service which promotes good customer service and effective working relationships. This will include: reparation of agendas and action logs, taking appropriate follow-up actions, management of specialist dental services payments processes, supporting the team with the management of contracts and projects, gathering information and managing communication and correspondence as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is responsible for delivering administration support for the Secondary Care Team which hold a portfolio of contracts that includes 11 Acute Trust contracts and 36 Integrated Minor Oral Surgery contracts and 5 Community Dental Services contracts across the 5 STP/ICS areas of Derbyshire, Nottinghamshire, Lincolnshire, Northamptonshire and Leicester, Leicestershire and Rutland.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the nature of the role, the successful applicant maybe required to attend some scheduled evening meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to work for the NHS England and NHS Improvement – Midlands to help shape and commission specialist dental services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details on the role, please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Claire Hames&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contract Manager, Secondary Dental Care/IMOS/CDS – East Midlands&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tel: 07783816176 or Email claire.hames@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Claire Hames&lt;/p&gt;
